data.description: You'll love this easy living, step saving one level. Perfect "Lock and Leave" opportunity for those on the go, or, if you're just tired of yard work. Quiet and peaceful East facing back yard adjoins community park (no rear neighbors!). Floor plan and all communal areas easily accommodate seniors. Central Meridian location makes for easy access to anywhere in the valley.
